properties.Name: Tarheel army missile plant
properties.description:
Massive abandoned missile plant. Huge wide open buildings and spaces, a ton of space to explore. Almost all of the old equipment has been cleared out, but there's still a ton of interesting things to see. VERY easy to be seen, only go at night. There is a hole in the fence behind the tractor trailers, next to the steakhouse. Wear a mask or better yet, a respirator. *Most* of the radiation signs, and all of the biohazard signs are fake.
Locations are approximate, especially if the pin is in a bigger building.
